        INPUT:

        - ``b`` -- :class:`DetAutomaton`  to concatenate
        - ``det``  -- (default: ``True``) - if True, determinize
        - ``simplify`` -- (default: ``True``) - if True and if det=True,
          prune and minimize
        - ``verb`` -- boolean (default: ``False``) if True, print
          debugging informations

        OUTPUT:

